South African June Gold Production Fell by 5.7% From Year Ago, Agency Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-11T09:30:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-11/south-african-june-gold-production-fell-by-5-7-from-year-ago-agency-says.html
South African gold production fell
5.7 percent in June from a year earlier, Jean-Pierre Terblanche,
a spokesman for  Statistics South Africa , said by phone from
 Pretoria  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
